      "date": "2020-07-16 15:37:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThe same issue is addressed by one of the UDSP patches: https://review.whamcloud.com/34351\n\nFurthermore, this patch has incorrect priority for lpni selection. Health should always be the first selection criteria.\n\nI would propose that, for master, we just use the UDSP patch. A separate patch should probably be made for b2_12 that is equivalent to the UDSP patch, but without the UDSP selection priority bits.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
