        },
        "subject": "LU-12288 lnet: preferred flag policy does not work",
        "message": "LU-12288 lnet: preferred flag policy does not work\n\nIf there are 2 peers and the both peers are preffered,\nthere are cases where the Preffered peer(the first one)\nis not selected(Preffered flag is ignored).\n\nWe fixed that route selection is in the following order.\n    1.Preferred\n    2.Health Value\n    3.Credits\n    4.Seq Number\n\nSigned-off-by: Tatsushi Takamura <takamr.tatsushi@jp.fujitsu.com>\nChange-Id: Ia32c6f099441cc466b7474d5e4fb09054755f11f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
